2.2  E-Commerce Negotiation Dataset

Description
This dataset contains buyer-seller negotiation dialogues set in a Unity3D virtual marketplace. The AI seller agent must simultaneously pursue commercial objectives (reaching a deal) and comply with social norms of politeness, honesty, and fairness. The dataset captures a range of negotiation dynamics including counter-offers, value bundling, floor-price disclosure, and alternative product offering. It is the most structured of the three scenarios, which explains the framework’s highest reasoning accuracy in this setting (0.91).

